self._do_memory_test(
    """
            <%namespace name="x">
                <%def name="a()">
                    this is x a
                </%def>
                <%def name="b()">
                    this is x b, and heres ${a()}
                </%def>
            </%namespace>

            ${x.a()}

            ${x.b()}
    """
    , 'this is x a this is x b, and heres this is x a', filters=flatten_result)
